reviews.text: I quite enjoyed their bbq pork and roast duck combo rice platter take out.   The rice was a little on the firm side for my taste tho.  I dont think you can go wrong eating in either.  Pricing are quite reasonable.

Lousy food, rude services, expensive prices.  Encountered a few occasions in this year their meat dishes not thoroughly cooked n with strong meat tendering chemical tastes. Interesting enough their waiters asked me what I wanted them to do when I told them their meats r still cold n uncooked.  I used to be their regular customer since childhood. Unfortunately no longer the same good old tastes like years ago.  Still can survive because of its glory history plus insufficient eateries around that area.  I won't visit this place anymore despite with all my good childhood memories, so sad I hv to give up this used to be good neighbourhood eatery.

叉燒腸：口感煙韌及滑口,唯沒有米香味,皮不是厚身那種,餡料則屬正常。
鳳爪排骨飯（大）：份量屬一位男仕吃那種,飯質地軟身,排骨和鳳爪亦是大路之作。
蝦餃：希望愈大,失望愈大,因為一吃落去就感覺到酸味,好明顯是壞掉的,就算賣相看來不錯。
茶：叫咗香片,茶太混濁,兼且有點搶喉,希望其它不是那麼差吧！
